---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Peer observation" lang="en">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Peer observation</h1>

    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
      Have you spotted an innovation, tool or practice among the platform's projects and would
      you like to learn more about it to implement it in your courses?
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8">
      Teachers who have agreed to open the door of their classroom to UNIGE colleagues indicate it
      on their project page (the “Peer observation” note). Contact them directly to suggest an
      observation or to get more information about their projects.
    </p>

    <a href="https://www.unige.ch/sea/ressources/observation-entre-pairs" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
       class="inline-block text-sm text-unige-red hover:underline">
      → Learn more about peer observation
    </a>
  </div>
</Base>
